":10153,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:08:30.000Z","msg":"我會揀premiere<br />\n<br />\n首先係adobe嘅軟件ecosystem<br />\n可以來回交替After Effects, Photoshop等<br />\n<br />\n其次係premiere嘅effects<br />\n有好多參數都可以adjust<br />\n比起以前AE、PR來回替換方便左好多<br />\n<br />\n比較翻FCP<br />\n<br />\n介面同使用體驗上真係user - friendly<br />\n減少你剪片時候嘅雜亂感<br />\n而且係啲比較舊嘅Mac依然流暢運行<br />\n即使spec一般 preview基本上都唔會lag<br />\n<br />\n但係玩effects方面<br />\n基本上應付到部份project、vlog<br />\n但如果好深入咁去adjust<br />\n你始終都係覺得差少少<br />\n應付唔到大project<br />\n<br />\n當然以上都係主觀睇法<br />\n係透過我日常嘅體驗結論而黎<br />\n亦都唔代表個軟件真係好/唔好"},{"pid":"d683639f3390858ae9a7804037ba4e7ec6203354","tid":482720,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:22:06.000Z","msg":"Windows Premiere<br />\nMac FCP"},{"pid":"0ebf9be5f53699b6a6ae77ee6b954e8a7a15cb1c","tid":482720,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會揀premiere<br />\n<br />\n首先係adobe嘅軟件ecosystem<br />\n可以來回交替After Effects, Photoshop等<br />\n<br />\n其次係premiere嘅effects<br />\n有好多參數都可以adjust<br />\n比起以前AE、PR來回替換方便左好多<br />\n<br />\n比較翻FCP<br />\n<br />\n介面同使用體驗上真係user - friendly<br />\n減少你剪片時候嘅雜亂感<br />\n而且係啲比較舊嘅Mac依然流暢運行<br />\n即使spec一般 preview基本上都唔會lag<br />\n<br />\n但係玩effects方面<br />\n基本上應付到部份project、vlog<br />\n但如果好深入咁去adjust<br />\n你始終都係覺得差少少<br />\n應付唔到大project<br />\n<br />\n當然以上都係主觀睇法<br />\n係透過我日常嘅體驗結論而黎<br />\n亦都唔代表個軟件真係好/唔好</blockquote><br />\n大致認同,由其係講effects個方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7328e9b246179ad52f0e1f682b9bf1173a897b85","tid":482720,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:46:16.000Z","msg":"premiere"},{"pid":"a6fed40d542f5b4c56dca8d81ddbe9e12f0fe320","tid":482720,"uid":48631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我會揀premiere<br />\n<br />\n首先係adobe嘅軟件ecosystem<br />\n可以來回交替After 